    "slug": "high-power-electromagnetics-workshop",
    "absolute_slug": "https://memento.epfl.ch/event/high-power-electromagnetics-workshop",
    "lang": "en",
    "state": "Published",
    "description": "<p>The IEEE Switzerland EMC/MTT/AP joint chapter is organizing along with the EPFL, montena technology, and the URSI Swiss National Committee, the 2018 High Power Electromagnetics Workshop. It is a one-day meeting that will take place in Lausanne, the 5th of February 2018, and will focus on NEMP, IEMI, and Lightning Electromagnetics.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWe would like to invite you to participate to this workshop. The invited speakers will present lectures or short talks about their research or industrial activities. It constitutes a very good opportunity to review the ongoing work about HPE in Switzerland and neighboring countries, and to foster networking and future activities in this domain that has lost some attention during the past years.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\"https://events.vtools.ieee.org/m/48379\">More information and registration</a><br>\r\n <br>\r\nThe event is open to all interested public, you can also forward to your colleagues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.ieee.ch/assets/Uploads/Chapter_AP_MTT_EMC/HPEW-poster.pdf\">Download the poster of the event</a></p>",
